Trailforks,is,a,user,powered,mountain,biking,trail,database,for,Canada,It,includes,information,such,as,trail,locations,D,maps,trail,features,and,current,conditions,Trailforks,also,serves,as,a,platform,for,riding,associations,and,riders,to,log,work,done,on,trails,and,monitor,trail,issues,A,REST,based,API,enables,users,to,add,or,retrieve,trail,information,programmatically